prompt: Photorealistic still life, 16:9. A single, polished silver sphere sits on a dark, matte black surface. Dramatic chiaroscuro lighting from a single, focused spotlight highlights the sphere's smooth gradient from bright white to deep black, showcasing a full range of values. The background is out of focus, a deep, rich black, emphasizing the sphere and its reflected light. Depth of field is shallow, creating a sense of intimacy and focus on the value transitions. --ar 16:9
name: pictures-of-value-in-art-image-1.png

prompt: Dramatic landscape, 16:9. A vast, snow-covered mountain range under a stormy sky. The foreground features jagged, dark rocks contrasted against the bright white snow. The sky is a gradient of grays, from almost black storm clouds to lighter, almost white patches breaking through. The lighting is diffused and dramatic, highlighting the contrast between light and shadow on the mountains. Use Ansel Adams style black and white photography as an inspiration. --ar 16:9

prompt: Conceptual art, 16:9. A photorealistic painting of an open book lying on a wooden table. Each page displays a different value scale, ranging from pure black to pure white. The left page is a smooth gradient, the right page is broken into distinct blocks of value. Soft, natural light illuminates the book from the left, casting subtle shadows. The background is blurred, with only hints of a cozy, inviting room. The style is reminiscent of classic Dutch still life. --ar 16:9

prompt: Urban scene, 16:9. A photorealistic photograph of a rainy city street at night. Neon signs reflect in the wet pavement, creating a vibrant display of color and light.
